{
    "poem_title": "- CVII - Al mismo asunto ",
    "corpus": "adso",
    "manually_checked": true,
    "author": "Joseph de Litala y Castelvi",
    "stanzas": [
        {
            "stanza_number": 1,
            "stanza_type": "cuarteto",
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 1,
                    "n": "1",
                    "line_text": "Si el Ebro en su corriente caudaloso",
                    "metrical_pattern": "-+---+---+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 2,
                    "n": "2",
                    "line_text": "compasivo al dolor de nuestros males,",
                    "metrical_pattern": "--+--+---+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 3,
                    "n": "3",
                    "line_text": "en lágrimas nos trueca sus cristales",
                    "metrical_pattern": "-+---+---+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 4,
                    "n": "4",
                    "line_text": "no es Río, es un peñasco pavoroso.",
                    "metrical_pattern": "++++-+---+-"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Si el Ebro en su corriente caudaloso\ncompasivo al dolor de nuestros males,\nen lágrimas nos trueca sus cristales\nno es Río, es un peñasco pavoroso."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 2,
            "stanza_type": "cuarteto",
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 5,
                    "n": "5",
                    "line_text": "Las sombras pisa del común reposo,",
                    "metrical_pattern": "-+-+---+-+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 6,
                    "n": "6",
                    "line_text": "al que heredando tantos timbres reales,",
                    "metrical_pattern": "---+-+-+-+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 7,
                    "n": "7",
                    "line_text": "los arcos esperaban triunfales,",
                    "metrical_pattern": "-+---+---+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 8,
                    "n": "8",
                    "line_text": "Marte Español, y vencedor glorioso.",
                    "metrical_pattern": "+--+---+-+-"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Las sombras pisa del común reposo,\nal que heredando tantos timbres reales,\nlos arcos esperaban triunfales,\nMarte Español, y vencedor glorioso."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": "terceto",
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "n": "9",
                    "line_text": "El grande Baltasar, rayo primero",
                    "metrical_pattern": "-+---++--+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "n": "10",
                    "line_text": "del Júpiter Austriaco de España,",
                    "metrical_pattern": "-+---+--+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 11,
                    "n": "11",
                    "line_text": "mayor estrella, si mayor lucero.",
                    "metrical_pattern": "-+-+---+-+-"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "El grande Baltasar, rayo primero\ndel Júpiter Austriaco de España,\nmayor estrella, si mayor lucero."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 4,
            "stanza_type": "terceto",
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 12,
                    "n": "12",
                    "line_text": "De la Iberia el terror de la Campaña",
                    "metrical_pattern": "--+--+---+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 13,
                    "n": "13",
                    "line_text": "aquel que abandonado el limpio acero,",
                    "metrical_pattern": "-+---+-+-+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 14,
                    "n": "14",
                    "line_text": "de esplendor Celestial su frente baña.",
                    "metrical_pattern": "--+--+-+-+-"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "De la Iberia el terror de la Campaña\naquel que abandonado el limpio acero,\nde esplendor Celestial su frente baña."
        }
    ]
}